title: tokyohd
author: tokyohd
content: BabyDoge Achieves New Big Community Milestone! On April 29, this number was still at the 1.3 million level, while in February it stood at 1 million. Thus, over the past 5 months, the growth has been nearly half a million Twitter followers.This is not the only milestone reached by BabyDoge recently. As reported by U.Today, earlier this week the number of the BabyDoge circulating supply was finally verified by CoinMarketCap. Besides, the BabyDoge holder number has spiked to reach an all-time high of 1,550,000 addresses.At press-time, the price of the meme token is holding at $0.000000001177, showing a decline by 3.46 percent in the past 24 hours. Source Link: https://u.today/babydoge-achieves-new-big-community-milestone I love BabyDoge. I expect big profits from babydoge coins in the future. Do you agree with me?

comments.author: bittick
comments.body: Twitter followers meant nothing, this can be bunch of bots that follow this meme token that has no value. The babydoge army was also very annoying. With multi billions of supply and this is not a big surprise for me but the total active wallet must become the main thing to determine this. You can expect a big profit in the future but not so big like when elon was hyping the meme token
